               <msContents>
                  <summary>A copy, in the hand of Menches, Komogrammateus (village secretary) of Kerkeosiris, of the indictment of certain officials (most likely village secretaries) from three divisions of the nome concerned with the crops, who have apparently made false reports. Appended is a much mutilated note concerning the decision of the superior official upon the case.</summary>
